  "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/questions/1295424/how-to-convert-float-to-int-with-java",
  "title" : "How to convert float to int with Java",
  "body" : "<p>I used the following line to convert float to int, but it's not as accurate as I'd like:</p>\n\n<pre><code> float a=8.61f;\n int b;\n\n b=(int)a;\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>The result is : <code>8</code> (It should be <code>9</code>)</p>\n\n<p>When <code>a = -7.65f</code>, the result is : <code>-7</code> (It should be <code>-8</code>)</p>\n\n<p>What's the best way to do it ?</p>\n"
